(February 9, 1967)

(Republished)

The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. John Ross, Appellant.

Order entered on April 15, 1966, unanimously affirmed. The order of this court entered on January 31, 1967 [27 A D 2d 707] is vacated. No opinion. Concur— Botein, P. J., Stevens, Capozzoli, McNally and Witmer, JJ.
